sailant approaches you with their bra pulled down, revealing one of their nipples. You can''t help but stare, mouth agape, as they walk toward you. As they near, you notice they are lactating. Suddenly, they give their nipple a quick pinch and tug, squirting their breast milk into your mouth! You swallow it to avoid choking. You suddenly feel a stronger magical aura about you. You also notice that your nipples are now puffy and swollen. Your breasts feel heavier, fuller. You give them a soft squeeze and they feel... like something is sloshing within? After a moment, milk starts to dribble from your inflamed nipples.', N'You approach your target with your bra pulled down, revealing one of your nipples. They can''t help but stare, mouth agape, as you walk toward them. Suddenly, you give your nipple a quick pinch and tug, squirting your breast milk into their mouth! Almost choking on it, they''re forced to swallow. You smile as you notice that their nipples are now puffy and swollen. You can''t help but giggle when you see them discover that they their swollen and heavy-looking breasts! After a moment, milk starts to dribble from their newly puffy nipples.', NULL, NULL, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), 1, -10, 0, 0, 0, 0, -10, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0)
