You feel a hint of magic as their lips briefly connect with your skin, leaving you dumbfounded as they pull away. You feel a strange warmth wash over you, and as you look around yourself to see if anything out of the ordinary is going on, you notice—their lips! There is something unusual about their ruby-red lips; the way they smile at you as you look at them in confusion, the way the light reflects on those hot lips of theirs... it drives you crazy! What wouldn''t you do for just another kiss? 
You absent-mindedly note that your cheek still tingles with magic... Maybe you should clean off that kiss mark? On the other hand... you think, as the center of your attention blows you another kiss, their red lips looking so inviting... Maybe you should leave it there for ten or twenty minutes or so. A silly smile spreads across your face as you trace those alluring lips with your eyes, and you conclude: what''s the harm in indulging in a little fantasy now and then? And what''s the worst that could happen? After all, you''d be sure to receive a lot of kisses if you ended up in your opponent''s possession...', NULL, NULL, N'You smile as you watch your intended mark go about their business, and pull out your trusty ruby-red lipstick—once a mage very much like your current target. You pull the cap off and twist up the woman-shaped lipstick, literally feeling joy radiating from her as you apply her generously to your lips—her one greatest obsession, an obsession that will soon be shared by your latest victim, albeit briefly! Your lips coated with your former enemy, you turn towards your current one and walk up to them, placing a kiss on their cheek before they have time to react! You smile at their dumbstruck expression as you pull away from them, their eyes almost immediately drawn to your lips. Seeing their hand slowly move upwards to wipe away that magic kiss mark, you quickly blow them another kiss, once again bringing their attention back to where it belongs: your lips. After what you assume to be a brief internal struggle, they lower their hand and a silly smile spreads across their face as they seem content to trace your lips with their eyes.', NULL, NULL, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 