nse... more magical? "You may think I''m a dreamer, but I won''t be the only one.  Today you''re gonna join me... we''re gonna have a lot of fun!"  And suddenly... well, the hate isn''t gone from your mind, but your actions feel constrained; it''s going to be very difficult to break through your new pacifist thoughts and cast for a short while, at least until you can get her thoughts out of your head.', NULL, NULL, N'You start singing for your opponent:  "Imagine there''s no magic, it won''t be hard at all.  If you have need of clothing... just go shopping at the mall."  They aren''t listening. "Imagine Vamp and Kitsu, sharing all the streets..."  They go right on ignoring your peaceful protest, continuing their warmongering ways.  Hmpfh.  Even this level of violence pains you, though it IS for a good cause; you give them a chance for peace, subtly altering the final verse:  "You may think I''m a dreamer, but I won''t be the only one.  Today you''re gonna join me... we''re gonna have a lot of fun!"  And as their hands fall to their sides, you sense that it may have worked...', NULL, NULL, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), 1, 0, 0, -15, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, -15, 0, 0, 0)
