', 0, NULL, 0, 2, 12, NULL, N'An ice queen stands before you, one with the wind and sky.  While at first you thought she was the good girl; concealing, not feeling, not letting you know about the pitiless storm swirling inside her, but now you know.  Her power flurries through the air into the ground, her magic spiraling in frozen fractals all around you, binding you to the spot. The cold isn''t bothering HER anyway as she laughs at your predicament,  your extreme difficulty of movement.  One thought crystallizes like an icy blast as you examine your bulkiest, heaviest item.  Perhaps you could break free, summoning the strength to rise from your icy prison like the break of dawn. If only you would let it go...
', NULL, NULL, N'Your icy heart used to know mercy, but that perfect girl is now gone.  There is no right, no wrong, no rules for you; pitilessly eyeing the soon-to-be-victim before you, you decide it''s time to see what you can do.  Your power flurries through the air into the ground, your magic spiraling in frozen fractals all around the unfortunate mage.  You laugh remorselessly, one with the wind and sky as you see the storm rage around them. If they test their limits they may be able to break through, though that item they are carrying looks so, so heavy – perhaps if they let it go?
', NULL, NULL, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, -30, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0)
