ana? In fear of your life, you leash out and the sudden thrust of one of your arms breaks her trance and feeding frenzy. As she stumbles back briefly, you face her again, ready to defend your life. Who would have guessed that her embrace could be more scary than her claws or teeth. Yet you realize the fight didn''t become easier just now. You feel drained and might not be able to engage in a long distance fight anymore. Maybe you should escape?', NULL, NULL, NULL, N'You leap towards your target, driven wild by your thirst. As you close in, you enwrap his body for a moment and shift your position behind him. Even though you have him prone for about a second, your goal is not to wound or kill him. Instead you feel the natural aura eminating from his body and soul and can''t resist the urge. The time seems to slow down, as your body slowly absorbs the very essence of magic from him, bestowing a feeling you haven''t felt since your... transformation; a sense of life. Only the sudden thrust of your enemies arm breaks your trance and feeding frenzy and as you stumble briefly to your back, he faces you again. But this time maybe a little... drained.', N'You leap towards your target, driven wild by your thirst. As you close in, you enwrap her body for a moment and shift your position behind her. Even though you have her prone for about a second, your goal is not to wound or kill her. Instead you feel the natural aura eminating from her body and soul and can''t resist the urge. The time seems to slow down, as your body slowly absorbs the very essence of magic from her, bestowing a feeling you haven''t felt since your... transformation; a sense of life. Only the sudden thrust of your enemies arm breaks your trance and feeding frenzy and as you stumble briefly to your back, she faces you again. But this time maybe a little... drained.', CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(1