', 0, NULL, 0, 3, 9, NULL, N'"Beast!" orders the enemy mage, "It is time to play.  Go assault that one. Take as much time as you need, but neither you nor they may reach climax.  Understand?"  Apparently it does; before you even realize you are the tentacle beast''s target, it is upon you, binding your body and beginning to tease your erogenous zones.  You notice time around you seeming to slow down; the beast''s master and others around seem to move in slow-motion, then they stop entirely.  You unwisely gasp as you realize the trouble you are in, and a tentacle enters your mouth.  The beast continues rubbing you, penetrating you, fucking you for what seems like hours! Though true to your enemy''s words, not only does it not reach climax, but whatever magic is slowing down time prevents you from doing the same.  Eventually, your struggles against the beast cease, as you continue to be pounded for what seems like hours. It finally withdraws and time seems to start moving normally around you again, though your will to fight is still broken.', NULL, NULL, N'That enemy mage looks a bit dangerous, you think it''s time to knock them down a peg or two.  "Beast!" you order your tentacled companion, "It is time to play.  Go assault that one. Take as much time as you need, but neither you nor they may reach climax.  Understand?"  It does; before your target even realizes what you intend, it is upon them, binding their body, beginning to tease their erogenous zones. Wanting to give your pet all the time it needs, you summon a bubble of slow-time around your victim.  Once it takes hold, you can see – at incredible speed – the beast''s assault; all sorts of rubbing, penetrating, sheer fucking, yet neither the beast nor your victim ever finds release.  After a few minutes – subjectively hours for them – you dispel the bubble.  Your opponent sighs in defeat as the beast withdraws, their will to fight obviously broken ...
', NULL, NULL, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), 0, 0, 0, -5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, -5, -10, 0, 0)
