 N'Deeply grieved by the pain of your counterpart, you decide to share your bond with nature and life with him. Tapping into your abundant magic, you create a magical link between your two hearts and souls. As your feelings of compassion and coexistence reach him, so does your magic. Slowly your serene feelings and compassion heals his soul, as your bond with nature heals his body. You just wish this could last and maybe he could be convinced to join you in peace, together as part of your own little village of fae; a brother... or fairy sister perhaps?', N'Deeply grieved by the pain of your counterpart, you decide to share your bond with nature and life with her. Tapping into your abundant magic, you create a magical link between your two hearts and souls. As your feelings of compassion and coexistence reach her, so does your magic. Slowly your serene feelings and compassion heals her soul, as your bond with nature heals her body. You just wish this could last and maybe she could be convinced to join you in peace, together as part of the sisters and daughters of your own little village of fae.', CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), 1, 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 10, 0, 0, 0)
