sh into you. Not any evil magic, or curses, not even magical trickery. Pure, undiluted mana flows into you and charges you up completely. You try to thank the creature and step away, but it''s not letting you! More and more magic flows into you, filling your circuits up completely. And the torrent isn''t stopping. Moments later your circuits burst with a loud crackle and a violent flash, leaving you drained of almost all magical energy. You watch the strange creature slip away, very satisfied with itself.', NULL, NULL, N'You nudge the bloated mana-sucking parasite that''s been calling itself your pet towards your target. Honestly... Drained you dry repeatedly and doesn''t want to share even though it''s about to burst? Well, you''re not about to be hit by another one of the Manta Ray''s mana pulses - not after the first time. It takes almost all of your magic to get the glowy balloon-like creature to move away, but you''re rewarded by a massive flash and a sharp, zapping noise. Looks like your opponent has just had their magical circuits fried by an overdose of mana. That should teach them to hug strange pets.', NULL, NULL, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, -30, 0, 0, 0, 0)
