llows. Then, as suddenly as the pleasure began, it halts and you find yourself on your knees in a daze. His laughter fills the room as his thoughts fill your head. “Enjoy just a sliver of what I have to offer.”  As the lust disappears and you stand, his final thought whispers into your ear. “Perhaps when we are finished you can find me later to sate your… desires.”', NULL, NULL, N'-', NULL, NULL, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, -5, 0, 0, 0, -10, 0, 0, 0)
