red his natural aura with you; something that will protect you from others... and sadly your enemies from your own spells. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, N'You look around and see him besides you. For a moment you think about his situation and decide he has suffered enough in this town. As a gesture of friendship and peace, you decide to offer him just a sliver of your magical protection, to shield him for a time. It doesn''t matter if he is a friend or enemy, he is a person. And every person deserves a chance to live. Silently you lift your magical sword in front of your forehead with the cross-guard at its center. With your shield tucked below your chest, you focus yourself and transmit the very essence of your own protective magic into the blade of your sword. Once you are certain to be ready, you move your blade in one swift manner to point its tip towards him. As the magic leaves your blade, it is accompanied by your honest feelings of compassion and honor and soon enshrouds him in a warm light. For now he will be ready to face any threat, for himself or for his friends. Of course your aura will keep him from harming anyone else too. Something you are perfectly fine with. All should live together in this town, peacefully.', N'You look around and see her besides you. For a moment you think about her situation and decide she has suffered enough in this town. As a gesture of friendship and peace, you decide to offer her just a sliver of your magical protection, to shield her for a time. It doesn''t matter if she is a friend or enemy, she is a person. And every person deserves a chance to live. Silently you lift your magical sword in front of your forehead with the cross-guard at its center. With your shield tucked below your chest, you focus yourself and transmit the very essence of your own protective magic into the blade of your sword. Once you are certain to be ready, you move your blade in one swift manner to point its tip towards her. As the magic leaves your blade, it