your mirthful memories of yourself. You never felt so confident in yourself as you are now and you are sure not even this town could take it from you. Though why do you feel so drained all of a sudden?', NULL, NULL, NULL, N'A certain man with a weird gaze catches your attention and you wonder if he is truly himself. For a moment you consider to ask him about his troubles, but you ultimately decide to just share a bit of his own happiness with him. Gently you focus your inherent light magic and step besides him to suddenly and surprising caress his cheek. He looks at you in shock for a second, but his soon relaxed and melancholic gaze tells you he delves deep into the beautiful memories he had once or are the new essence of who he became inside this town. Nevertheless, he soon seems to be lost in his mirth and reclaims a stronger grasp on his current identity. Satisfied you remove your gauntlet in a tender stroke and disengage him. If he wasn''t at ease with his current self, you are certain he will be from now on. ', N'A certain woman with a weird gaze catches your attention and you wonder if she is truly herself. For a moment you consider to ask her about her troubles, but you ultimately decide to just share a bit of her own happiness with her. Gently you focus your inherent light magic and step besides her to suddenly and surprising caress her cheek. She looks at you in shock for a second, but her soon relaxed and melancholic gaze tells you she delves deep into the beautiful memories she had once or are the new essence of who she became inside this town. Nevertheless, she soon seems to be lost in her mirth and reclaims a stronger grasp on her current identity. Satisfied you remove your gauntlet in a tender stroke and disengage her. If she wasn''t at ease with her current self, you are certain she will be from now on. ', CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), 1, 0, 0, -5, 0, 0, -10, 0, 0, -15, 0, 0, 0, 0)
