e pain.  You raise your finger to your mouth to nurse the wound which seems to momentarily help.  But any attempt to concentrate on a spell brings the memories flooding back, hampering your aim and ability to properly formulate the spell without the risk of misfiring.  ', NULL, NULL, NULL, N'You smile meekly at the mage standing off in the distance.  A sweet perfume emanates from the bloom atop your head, the wind carrying the scent in their direction.  He starts to approach you, drawn in by your alluring aroma.  As he reaches out a hand to touch your arm, his finger pricks a thorn, hand reeling back in pain.  You watch him double back, wrestling with the memory of what he has just experienced, his focus shattered.  A soft giggle escapes your crimson lips, confident this warning will keep you safe as he struggles to concentrate on any spells he may try to use against you.', N'You smile meekly at the mage standing off in the distance.  A sweet perfume emanates from the bloom atop your head, the wind carrying the scent in their direction.  She starts to approach you, drawn in by your alluring aroma.  As she reaches out a hand to touch your arm, her finger pricks a thorn, hand reeling back in pain.  You watch her double back, wrestling with the memory of what she has just experienced, her focus shattered.  A soft giggle escapes your crimson lips, confident this warning will keep you safe as she struggles to concentrate on any spells she may try to use against you.', CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CA