ou have become.

', NULL, NULL, NULL, N'You sense promise in this youngling - perhaps incineration is premature. You decide to mark him instead, and corrupt his humanity with your immortal darkness. You touch his shoulder, and split the weak shell of his being with the wild magicks of your homeland. You feel him grow strong with your power, his flaws mended by your strength and his purity destroyed by your corruption. You are so impressed by his ability to take in your energy, that you are tempted to turn him permanently... but then he might actually present a threat... perhaps letting your power wear off is for the best.', N'You sense promise in this youngling - perhaps incineration is premature. You decide to mark her instead, and corrupt her humanity with your immortal darkness. You touch her shoulder, and split the weak shell of her being with the wild magicks of your homeland. You feel her grow strong with your power, her flaws mended by your strength and her purity destroyed by your corruption. You are so impressed by her ability to take in your energy, that you are tempted to turn her permanently... but then she might actually present a threat... perhaps letting your power wear off is for the best.', CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), 1, 0, 0, 20, 0, 0, 10, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0)
