 at her. "Alright. We can play for a bit." The dog girl perks up and smiles wide, her tail beginning to wag fast. "Yay!" What harm could come from playing with this cute dog girl?', NULL, NULL, NULL, N'You walk around the town with a ball in your hand, feeling rather bored.  Playing catch is fun, but it would be nice to have a fun new toy. As you walk you see a mage walking down the road and your tail begins to wag as you run over to him. "Hey there! Do you wanna play?" You ask him, holding the ball out towards him. Without responding, he begins to walk away. Your tail stops wagging and your ears droop. You look sadly at the mage''s back. "Oh...okay then..." The mage stops in his tracks and turns around. He looks at you and looks like he might say something when he sighs and smiles. Your face breaks into a large smile and your tail wags as you run over to the mage. You''re gonna have a lot of fun playing catch with him before turning him into your next squeak toy!', N'You walk around the town with a ball in your hand, feeling rather bored. Playing catch is fun, but it would be nice to have a fun new toy. As you walk you see a mage walking down the road and your tail begins to wag as you run over to her. "Hey there! Do you wanna play?" You ask her, holding the ball out towards her. Without responding, she begins to walk away. Your tail stops wagging and your ears droop. You look sadly at the mage''s back. "Oh...okay then..." The mage stops in her tracks and turns around. She looks at you and looks like she might say something when she sighs and smiles. Your face breaks into a large smile and your tail wags as you run over to the mage. You''re gonna have a lot of fun playing catch with her before turning her into your next squeak toy!', CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 