Its impressive wingspan serves to make it look all the more intimidating, although considering what the wings are attached to, it is doubtful they could be used for flight in these skies. Its wings are not the only thing that suggests this creature was never intended to walk the earth: its breathing is heavy, the occasional pained grunt tells you that it''s only with difficulty that the beast is even able to sustain itself on this plane.
