ing your mind from any further assault you take a few steps back and huff, the cabbit still smiling at you. If you stick around for too long you know he''ll have you eventually, your mental shield already waning. You turn and stomp away, no way are you about to tussle with some freakish radioactive hypnocat. Rabbit? Gah, whatever.', NULL, CAST(100.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), N'male', N'full', N'', N'cocky_cabbit_boy_Aurora_Ryall.jpg', 0, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(18, 2)), 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, -5, 0, 5, 0)
